        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎵 TEMPO</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">9 pts · T=1, E=1, M=3, P=3, O=1 · M+P combo</p></div>
