        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Clock words house the <span class="text-white font-medium">two rarest tiles in one word</span>. QUARTZ is the only common English word that uses both Q=10 and Z=10 together. Memorise this — it's the single highest-scoring natural word you can play without a bingo bonus.</p>
